                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The target can understand all words regardless of language and also speak the languages of other creatures. When in a mixed group of creatures, each time the target speaks, it can choose a creature and speak in a language that creature understands, even if the target doesn't know what language that is.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (7th)</strong> The duration is 8 hours.</p>"
